</P>
<P>
Kharrazi, who arrived in the Saudi capital Saturday for a short
visit, said upon arrival that the leaders of the two countries are
convinced that bilateral ties must be boosted on the basis of the
mutual understanding at the Islamic and regional levels.
</P>
<P>
He also delivered a letter from Iranian President Mohammad
Khatami to Saudi Crown Prince and Deputy Prime Minister Prince
Abdullah Ibn Abdul-Aziz. But he declined to reveal the
content of the letter.
</P>
